extends layout

block content

    // Content Header (Page header)
    .content-header.sty-one
        h1 Dashboard - Overview
        a.twitter-share-button(href='https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Great%20info%20about%20ETHO%20protocol.%20Check%20out%20this%20page.')
            | Tweet ths page


        ol.breadcrumb
            li
                a(href='#') Home
            li
                i.fa.fa-angle-right
                | Dashboard - Overview
    // Main content
    .content
        // Small boxes (Stat box)
        .row
            .col-lg-3.col-sm-6.col-xs-12
                .info-box.bg-green.text-white
                    span.info-box-icon.bg-transparent
                        i.ti-wallet.text-white
                    .info-box-content
                        h6.info-box-text.text-white ETHO circulating supply
                        h1.text-white= data.supply
                        span.progress-description.text-white  ETHO
                    // /.info-box-content
                // /.info-box
        // /.col
        // /.row
        // Main row
        script(src="/dist/js/chart.js")
        .row
            .col-md-6.d-flex
                .card.w-100
                    .card-body
                        h4.card-title.text-black Supply distribution
                        .info-box
                            .m-t-2
                                p !{chart1}
            .col-md-6.d-flex
                .card.w-100
                    .card-body
                        h4.card-title.text-black Information
                        .info-box
                            .m-t-2
                                p The overview dashboard provides a breakdown on the ETHO circulating supply. The supply is limited to around 70 Mio with then a annual inflation at 3%.
                                | The supply can be broken down into 5 pillars
                                ul
                                    li Wrapped ETHO
                                    | This is ETHO being wrapped on ETH in order to be traded on Kucoin and other exchanges using wrapped ETHO
                                    li Nodes
                                    | ETHO locked in nodes as collateral
                                    li Development fund
                                    | The development generated by ETHO according to the moneytary policy
                                    li Exchanges
                                    | Funds being in the wallets of exchanges like Kucoin, STEX, Probit, Graviex and Mercatox
                                    li HODL
                                    | ETHO locked into private accounts

                        h4.card-title.text-black Monetary policy
                            .info-box
                                .m-t-2
                                    img(src='/dist/img/financial_policy_3.png', width='100%')





            // /.content
        .row
            .col-lg-12.col-xlg-12
                .info-box
                    .d-flex.flex-wrap
                        div
                            h4.text-black Dev account with multisig in ETHO over 30 days
                            p The dev account account gets refilled by the blockchain emission schedule and depleted by council decisions
                                a(href='https://explorer.ethoprotocol.com/address/0xBA57dFe21F78F921F53B83fFE1958Bbab50F6b46/transactions', target='_blank') (Addr: 0xBA57dFe21F78F921F53B83fFE1958Bbab50F6b46/transactions)

                    .m-t-2
                        p !{chart2b}

        .row
            .col-lg-12.col-xlg-12
                .info-box
                    .d-flex.flex-wrap
                        div
                            h4.text-black Masternode account in ETHO over 7 days
                            p The masternode account gets refilled by the blockchain emission schedule and depleted by the daily payments for masternodes
                                a(href='https://explorer.ethoprotocol.com/address/0x00C41297cCEbe446AAbc154F32b16aEDE14E50aB', target='_blank') (Addr: 0x00C41297cCEbe446AAbc154F32b16aEDE14E50aB)
                    .m-t-2
                        p !{chart3}


        .row
            .col
                p Compared to other coins, the supply of ETHO is fairly limited and will be a basis for a higher evaluation per coin. ETHO is a minable coin with proof of work.
                | Ethp protocol is a minable coin based on Ethereum and incorporates IPFS in a master node concept.
                | Currently Etho protocol provide 3 master node tiers, reach generating a revenue for node holders of 10%.
                | More information can be found here:
                ul
                    li Etho protocol website
                    a(href="https://ethoprotocol.com")  https://ethoprotocol.com
                    li Etho protocol documentation
                    a(href="https://ethoprotocol.com")  https://docs.ethoprotocol.com
